      "para_id": "Q001868.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Ibbi-Suen , the god of his land , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , presented this ( seal ) to Suen-abušu , the cup-bearer , his friend as crown prince ."
    }
